An '''eCompass''' is a tilt compensated electronic [[compass]] utilizing an [[accelerometer]] and a [[magnetometer]]. A number of manufacturers, including [[Motorola]], make ecompasses. eCompasses are also found in some laptops such as the [http://store.hp.com/us/en/pdp/hp-spectre-x360-13-ae052nr HP Spectre]

